    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:1.2",
          "pli": "Atha kho sambahulā satullapakāyikā devatāyo abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. ",
          "en": "Then, late at night, several glorious deities of the Satullapa Group, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, and stood to one side. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:1.3",
          "pli": "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: ",
          "en": "Standing to one side, one deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:2.1",
          "pli": "“Saddhā dutiyā purisassa hoti, ",
          "en": "“Faith is a person’s partner. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:2.2",
          "pli": "No ce assaddhiyaṃ avatiṭṭhati; ",
          "en": "If faithlessness doesn’t linger, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:2.3",
          "pli": "Yaso ca kittī ca tatvassa hoti, ",
          "en": "fame and renown are theirs, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:2.4",
          "pli": "Saggañca so gacchati sarīraṃ vihāyā”ti. ",
          "en": "and when they discard this corpse they go to heaven.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:3.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi: ",
          "en": "Then another deity recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:4.1",
          "pli": "“Kodhaṃ jahe vippajaheyya mānaṃ, ",
          "en": "“Give up anger, get rid of conceit, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:4.2",
          "pli": "Saṃyojanaṃ sabbamatikkameyya; ",
          "en": "and get past all the fetters. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:4.3",
          "pli": "Taṃ nāmarūpasmimasajjamānaṃ, ",
          "en": "Clingings don’t torment one who has nothing, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:4.4",
          "pli": "Akiñcanaṃ nānupatanti saṅgā”ti. ",
          "en": "not clinging to name and form.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:5.1",
          "pli": "“Pamādamanuyuñjanti, ",
          "en": "“Fools and unintelligent people "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:5.2",
          "pli": "bālā dummedhino janā; ",
          "en": "devote themselves to negligence. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:5.3",
          "pli": "Appamādañca medhāvī, ",
          "en": "But the intelligent protect diligence "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:5.4",
          "pli": "dhanaṃ seṭṭhaṃva rakkhati. ",
          "en": "as their best treasure. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:6.1",
          "pli": "Mā pamādamanuyuñjetha, ",
          "en": "Don’t devote yourself to negligence, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:6.2",
          "pli": "mā kāmarati santhavaṃ; ",
          "en": "or delight in sexual intimacy. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:6.3",
          "pli": "Appamatto hi jhāyanto, ",
          "en": "For if you’re diligent and practice absorption, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn1.36:6.4",
          "pli": "pappoti paramaṃ sukhan”ti. ",
          "en": "you’ll attain the highest happiness.”"
        }
      ],
